{"tid":605012,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[MTR奇遇]點樣可以撞返一個只係MTR見過一次既人??","createTime":"2018-03-25T09:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T06:42:46.000Z","uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cb78ae73f062f6d94b919ca2e2562265e5afbdb2","tid":605012,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">世間所有的相遇，都是久別重逢</span></div><br />\n話說兩個星期之前既星期五,個日唔駛OT準時走<br />\n大約6點廿幾分係MTR觀塘線某站上車返屋企<br />\n搭到鑽石山站個陣有個女仔上車<br />\n佢咩樣就唔形容,因為只係見過一次<br />\n但因為近距離見過佢,所以基本上認到佢面上某D特徵,如果有機會見返佢一定認到<br />\n搭到太子個陣我落車佢冇落<br />\n好想撞返佢,但連佢叫咩名都唔知,都唔知點搵好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有類似經歷??<br />\n咁既話,係唔係呢世都見唔返??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8c91987758df8f15319b3da8410b2502e60281","tid":605012,"uid":161341,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:23:58.000Z","msg":"好毒"},{"pid":"83c7122c160073c54142a07496a617fb46eaa4de","tid":605012,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a8c91987758df8f15319b3da8410b2502e60281","tid":605012,"uid":161341,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:23:58.000Z","msg":"好毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"我認我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f122c936503b84b0a928960ad7e29e7deb9a04f","tid":605012,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbbb791